# inference/requirements.in
#
# Human-readable, unpinned dependency list for the inference pod.
# This is the SOURCE FILE — do not install from this directly in production.
#
# To regenerate the locked requirements.txt:
#   uv pip compile requirements.in \
#       --python-version 3.11 \
#       --extra-index-url https://download.pytorch.org/whl/cu121 \
#       -o requirements.txt
#
# The Dockerfile installs from requirements.txt (pinned) for reproducibility.
# For local dev, use: uv sync  (from repo root or this directory)

